title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 23 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 23 2022
description:
Huge story from Clay and Buck's one-hour Mar-a-Lago interview yesterday: Trump thinks China will go after Taiwan. C&B say that's what should have been covered rather than fake news in which reporters "pretend" not to be able to read or understand. Biden's Ron Burgundy speech on Ukraine. On TV, Clay says Biden "reads this stuff now like it's a terrorist video." NYC to drop failed vaccine mandate. Buck says he is personally well aware of the pitfalls of his hometown's mandate. Viral video of reporter and his very involved mom that will give you a laugh.
